div.div: Released LightLog v2.0.0 - Enhanced Stability & Testing Framework of hesphoros/LightLogWriteImplWithPanel
Created new tag v2.0.0 in hesphoros/LightLogWriteImplWithPanel
更新项目名称和描述，添加简单演示程序，修正测试文件中的头文件引用

Add comprehensive logging test framework and modules
- Introduced a new logging test framework class `LogTestFramework` to manage and execute various logging functionality tests. - Implemented multiple test modules including: - `BasicLoggingTests`: Validates basic logging functionalities across different log levels. - `CallbackSystemTests`: Tests the callback mechanism for log events. - `RotationSystemTests`: Verifies log rotation functionality and configuration. - `CompressionSystemTests`: Checks the ZIP compression of log files and statistics. - `FilterSystemTests`: Tests the new filtering system including basic, composite, and integration tests. - `PerformanceTests`: Measures logging performance and asynchronous rotation capabilities. - Updated the main program to initialize the logging system and execute all test modules, providing a summary report at the end. - Fixed include path for `LightLogWriteImpl.h` in `LightLogWriteImpl.cpp`.
